---
import Base from "../layouts/Base.astro";
---

<Base
	title="Privacy Policy — FinCalc"
	description="FinCalc runs every calculation in your browser. We don't collect or store your financial inputs."
	path="/privacy"
>
	<section class="hero"><h1>Privacy Policy</h1></section>
	<div class="prose">
		<p>Last updated: 2026-06-14.</p>

		<h2>Your financial data never leaves your device</h2>
		<p>
			Every calculator on FinCalc runs entirely in your browser. The numbers you type — income,
			loan amounts, balances — are processed locally and are <strong>never transmitted to or stored
			on any server</strong>. We have no database of your inputs because we never receive them.
		</p>

		<h2>Analytics</h2>
		<p>
			We use privacy-friendly, aggregate analytics to understand which calculators are useful. This
			records page views and anonymous interaction events (such as "a calculation was completed"),
			with no personal identifiers and no cross-site tracking.
		</p>

		<h2>Advertising &amp; cookies</h2>
		<p>
			Pages may show display ads to keep the site free. Ad partners may set cookies; where required,
			a consent banner lets you accept or decline non-essential cookies, and we default to the
			minimum necessary. You can change your choice at any time.
		</p>

		<h2>No advice</h2>
		<p>
			FinCalc provides general-information calculators only. Nothing here is financial, investment,
			or tax advice. Always consult a qualified professional for decisions about your situation.
		</p>

		<h2>Contact</h2>
		<p>Questions about this policy? Reach us via the address listed on our site.</p>
	</div>
</Base>
